        <p><a href="https://portalpurwokerto.pikiran-rakyat.com/banyumas-raya/pr-1156090958/curug-pengantin-baturraden-curug-indah-yang-terpencil-dengan-mitos-romantis-agar-pasangan-setia-seumur-hidup?page=3" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Roboto,sans-serif"><span style="color:#1155cc"><span style="background-color:#ffffff"><u>https://portalpurwokerto.pikiran-rakyat.com/banyumas-raya/pr-1156090958/curug-pengantin-baturraden-curug-indah-yang-terpencil-dengan-mitos-romantis-agar-pasangan-setia-seumur-hidup?page=3</u></span></span></span></span></a><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Roboto,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="background-color:#ffffff">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>
        
